		<description>Arquebus gun made by improving Musket gun. The size of the caliber and the weight of the bullet are distinctive, and it has the power to blow off part of the body in the case of short range shooting. However, it is necessary to always carry around the arquebus rope and the fire rock, so the moving speed drops.</description>
